_sText:
THIS MAP PACK CONTAINS 2 ZOMBIE MOD MAPS


Contents:
This is a brand new map pack that contains two maps. First being "Zm An Jailbreak Miniv1", which is a small map that contains several useful points to help humans camp and cade with ease. Second is "Zm Zombie Beach Finale", which is a remake of the classic zm beach map by Vegeta. This version of the map contains newer areas and optimization to help improve game-play.

Support:
Optimization, 64 Player Support, Custom Textures (Jailbreak & Zombie Beach), Secret Areas

ChangeLog: (Current Version)
  • Zm An Jailbreak Miniv1 - Includes Radar/mini-map
